text: Jantsangiin Gantögs (born 12 April 1972) is a Mongolian archer. Gantögs competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics and the 2016 Summer Olympics.Jantsangiin Gantögs == References == Category:Mongolian archers Category:Olympians for Mongolia Category:1972 births Category:Living people
